<div class="quotetitle">vicious wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent"><br />Hm, interesting. I had in mind an asteroids-style rotation.<br /></div><br />This can certainly be done. Sprites can be rotated, it's just not automatic... The most common solution is to have different tiles for all posible rotations. Of course this limits the number of different objects you can have, since there are only 256 tiles available (512 if you use 8x16-pixel sprites, but 256 of those are shared with the background).<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=95">tokumaru</a> — Fri May 18, 2012 5:43 pm</p><hr />
